snippet.title: Best VGM 1050 - Kirby's Return to Dreamland - Aurora Area (Windy Waffles)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1247 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qrmzQOAASXo
Best VGM 1847 - https://youtu.be/eyiABstbKJE

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Nintendo Wii
Kirby's Return to Dreamland (2011)
Aurora Area
Jun Ishikawa & Hirokazu Ando
